<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.7">
<l>tuṉpamu miṉpamu mākiya ceyviṉai yāyula kaṅkaḷumā</l>
<l>yiṉpamil vennara kāki yiṉiyanal vāṉcuvark kaṅkaḷumāy</l>
<l>maṉpa luyirkaḷu mākip palapala māya mayakkukaḷā</l>
<l>liṉpuṟu mivviḷai yāṭṭuṭai yāṉaippeṟ ṟētumal lalilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having obtained the one who possesses this play that is pleasurable</l>
<l>through many many wondrous confusions, being the lasting many creatures,</l>
<l>being the pleasing good heavens, being the joyless hot hells,</l>
<l>being the worlds, being the deeds to be done that are sorrow and pleasure</l>
	<l>I am without any distress.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
